00:02:54.811 --> 00:02:57.500
Monday. The bigger Apple-A-I question — fallback-LLM partner at W-W-D-C — is

00:02:57.500 --> 00:03:00.190
still the live question, and Gurman's piece gestures at the roadmap without

00:03:00.190 --> 00:03:02.879
naming Anthropic, Google, or x-A-I. Six weeks to W-W-D-C. Anthropic. The application

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:05.568
